abstract: >-
  VerifiMind-PEAS (Prompt Engineering Attribution System) is a production-ready
  Model Context Protocol (MCP) server providing systematic multi-model AI validation
  capabilities. Developed over 87 days using the Genesis Prompt Engineering Methodology v2.0,
  this system provides comprehensive validation of AI-generated content across multiple
  LLM providers (Anthropic Claude, OpenAI GPT, Google Gemini, Perplexity).

  The system implements four core validation tools:
  1. analyze_prompt - Comprehensive prompt analysis
  2. validate_response - Multi-model response validation
  3. detect_hallucinations - Advanced hallucination detection
  4. suggest_improvements - Intelligent improvement recommendations

  Code quality: 98/100, Test pass rate: 100%, Production readiness: 85%.
